♪ My baby♪

22:05.060 --> 22:07.360
-♪ And the darkest hour...♪
-DANIEL: I now pronounce thee

22:07.410 --> 22:11.590
man and wife.

22:11.630 --> 22:15.500
♪ Each night
before you go to bed♪

22:15.550 --> 22:17.980
♪ My baby♪

22:18.030 --> 22:22.510
♪ Whisper a little prayer
for me♪

22:22.550 --> 22:24.600
♪ My baby♪

22:24.640 --> 22:28.250
♪ And tell♪

22:28.300 --> 22:32.000
♪ All the stars above♪

22:32.040 --> 22:35.090
♪ This is dedicated
to the one I love♪

22:35.130 --> 22:38.000
♪ Love can never be♪

22:38.050 --> 22:41.530
♪ Exactly like
we want it to be♪

