♪ I could be satisfied♪

22:45.450 --> 22:48.620
♪ Knowing you love me♪

22:48.670 --> 22:51.450
♪ And there's one thing
I want you to do♪

22:51.500 --> 22:55.280
♪ Especially for me♪

22:55.330 --> 22:57.590
♪ And it's something♪

